sequenceDiagram
  participant Client
  participant API
  participant RenderService
  participant DB
  participant Audit
  Client->>API: POST /assets/{id}/versions/{vid}/render
  API->>RenderService: render(versionId, inputs, save)
  RenderService->>DB: read version body and contract snapshot
  RenderService->>RenderService: substitute variables
  RenderService->>RenderService: compute diagnostics and rendered_hash
  alt save = true
    RenderService->>Audit: record render.saved
  end
  API-->>Client: RenderResult

